summary: Marvel Conan ahoy!
title: Marvel Conan ahoy!
body:
I’m a Conan the Barbarian fan.  I have been ever since I was old enough to appreciate the way Robert E. Howard crafted an adventure story.  Those who know me also know that I rather enjoy Marvel.  So, ever since I learned that Marvel had decided to take back the rights to Conan (which were being leased to Dark Horse Comics, according to my Local Comics Shop, who were putting them aside for me), I knew that it was only a matter of time before Marvel produced a crossover.

Marvel have not wasted time.  I’ve got a handful of issues of Marvel’s Conan (produced - bless them - by the same artists who had been working for Dark Horse), and suddenly, there he is, popping up in an Avengers story!

I am a happy, happy lady.
